I"><p>Since our 2.6.0 release, users can report an ad as inappropriate.</p>

<p>Below each ad, users will find this button:</p>

<p><img src="//docs.yclas.com/images/flag-inappropriate.png" alt="flag-inappropriate" /></p>

<p>By clicking this button, they will be redirected to the contact page, where Subject and Message are already filled with the necessary text.</p>

<p><img src="//docs.yclas.com/images/flag-inappropriate2.png" alt="flag-inappropriate2" /></p>

<p>An email will be sent to the administrator of the website in order to review the reported ad.</p>

